ComicInfo.Summary:
The mystery surrounding the new, female Deathblow deepens in the surprising miniseries from writer Alan Moore (TOM STRONG, PROMETHEA) and artist Jim Baikie (TOMORROW STORIES)! The new Deathblow is baffled by the strange things that are happening to her, and the advice of yet another Deathblow -- John Joe Cray -- is of no help at all. But even the dangers the two Deathblows face this issue pale in comparison to the deadly Judgment Cray, who has just taken notice of our confused heroine.
